    "body": "You could use something like this with the `$fill` module:\r\n```toml\r\nformat = \"\"\"╭─$os $username@$hostname$directory$git_branch$git_state$git_status$fill$all─╮\r\n╰─$character\"\"\"\r\nright_format= \"─╯\"\r\n````\r\n",
